  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de LXTask</title>



    <!--
    <para>

      First, fix some <quote>multiple definition</quote> issues exposed
      by GCC-10:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../lxtask-&lxtask-version;-gcc10_fix-1.patch</userinput></screen>
-->
<para>
      Installez <application>LXTask</application> en exécutant les commandes
suivantes&nbsp;:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Ce paquet n'a pas de suite de tests.
    </para>

    <para>
      Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem
class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

